    "Analysis processAlthough the main focus of this contribution is empirical insights, rather than substantially critiquing the approaches used, it is important to make the most of the NLP tools and recognise their strengths and limitations.",
    "As a result, we draw upon the approach set out by Heaton et al. [29] for best practice when using NLP tools for social media research.",
